data.description: 5K to Buy Down Rate. Up to 3K towards closing w/ Preferred Lender! Welcome to the amazing walking community of Trinity Townes! This 3 Story Townhome bestows functionality, beauty and convenience. The Main Level affords garage entry into the Flex Space (Rec Room, Gym or Bonus Room) that has a Walk Out Basement feel. The Charming Dual Stairway leads to the Upstairs as well as the Foyer! The 2nd Level affords ample natural ight and a Kitchen adorned with Upgraded Granite, Gas Range and an enormous Island. The Dining Area and Living Room complete the Open Concept! All the Sleep Quarters are located on the Third Level. The large Primary Bedroom shares no walls with the other 2 Bedrooms and is graced with Privacy. The En Suite has dual vanities and oversized shower. The Walk In Closet and Crown Molded Tray Ceiling has Upgraded Built-In Recess Lighting which add to the room! Perfectly located for Restaurants, Schools, Golf, Lake Wylie, Interstate Access and Shopping! Motivated NOW to close!!!
